{#
/**
 * @file
 * Default template for teaching reminder notifications.
 *
 * Available variables:
 * - $instructor: The instructor to be notified in this mail. Instance of <code>UserInterface</code>.
 * - $offering: The teaching event that this notification is about. Instance of <code>OfferingInterface</code>.
 * - $learner_names: An array of learner names/learner-group titles.
 * - $session_objectives: An array of session objectives. Instances of <code>ObjectiveInterface</code>.
 * - $course_objectives: An array of course objectives. Instances of <code>ObjectiveInterface</code>.
 * - $course_base_url: Link to the course management page in the Ilios frontend.
 */
#}
Dear {{ instructor.firstName }} {{ instructor.lastName }}:

This message is a reminder for your upcoming {{ offering.session.sessionType.title }} in this School of {{ offering.session.course.school.title }} course.

Course:   {{ offering.session.course.title }}
Session:  {{ offering.session.title }}
Date:     {{ offering.startDate|date('D M d, Y') }}
Time:     {{ offering.startDate|date('h:i a') }} - {{ offering.endDate|date('h:i a') }}
Location: {{ offering.room }}
Student Designation: {{ learners_names|join(';') }}.

The learning objectives listed for this session are:
{% for session_objective in session_objectives %}
    - {{ session_objective.title|striptags }}
{% endfor %}

The learning objectives listed for this course are:
{% for course_objective in course_objectives %}
    - {{ course_objective.title|striptags }}
{% endfor %}


A description of most classrooms, including maps, can be found at:
http://edtech.ucsf.edu/classroom-services/scheduling/classroom-features

For a complete review of the session details and its associated learning materials, visit the session details on your Ilios Calendar.
{{ course_base_url }}/#{{ offering.session.course.id }}.
If you would like to edit the details of this session and do not have editing rights in Ilios for this course please contact the School of {{ offering.session.course.school.title }}'s Curriculum Coordinator at {{ offering.session.course.school.ilios_administrator_email }}.


